---------Definition---------

The OR gate outputs 1 if at least one input is 1.

---------Properties---------

Output is low only when all inputs are low.

Also commutative and associative:

A OR B = B OR A

(A OR B) OR C = A OR (B OR C)

---------Applications---------

Fire alarms or motion detectors: triggers if any sensor detects an issue.

Used in data routing, signal switching, and decision-making circuits.
